snippet.title: Cosmic Royale - Launch Trailer - Steam & Epic Games Store
snippet.description:
Get ready to drift, jump and (try to) knock your opponents off the track in Cosmic Royale✨
Coming to Steam and Epic Games Store on December 12! 🎮

Add Cosmic Royale 🛒 to your wishlist:
👉 Epic Games Store: https://mtrvrs.com/CosmicEpic
👉 Steam: https://mtrvrs.com/CosmicSteam


Follow Cosmic Royale✨:

🖥️ Visit Cosmic Royale website - https://mtrvrs.com/Cosmic-Royale
👥 Join Cosmic Royale on Discord - https://mtrvrs.com/DiscordCosmic
💬 Follow Cosmic Royale on X - https://mtrvrs.com/XCosmic
